title: Darkstream: illegals and voter fraud
author: VD
content_html:
Tonight, at 7 PM Eastern, I’ll be discussing the God-Emperor’s war on voter fraud and the likely consequences therein. I’ll also be announcing Castalia’s new books… including a new audiobook.

UPDATE: The replay can be viewed here.

And as an added weekend bonus, I was on with Stefan Molyneux last night and it’s up already.
